Privacy policy

Personal data

   Hesper don't save personal data that could identify you, except the
   contact form that you are free to fill.

   Information sent by the contact form (identity, email address, phone
   number) are only used by Hesper to meet your demands.

   This information isn't stored in a database. They are only used to
   contact you to meet your demands and are not sold in any way to third
   parties.

Analytics

   In order to optimize the website "www.hesper.fr" based on applications
   of its visitors, Hesper counts the number of visits, the number of
   pages browsed and visitor activity on the website "www.hesper.fr".

   To do this, we use the statistics tool PIWIK, which generates a cookie
   with a unique identifier, whose shelf life is limited to 13 months.

   We also are capturing your IP address, to determine the city from which
   you are connected. The IP address is anonymized immediately after being
   used. So we can't in any case find by this means a person.

   The data collected are not sold to third parties or used for other
   commercial purposes.

Why we chose to use PIWIK

   Today respect for privacy on the Internet is a major issue for many
   users, webmasters and companies.

   In comparison to other analytics third party, PIWIK lets us :
    1. Manage data we collect. Data are saved in our own database and will
       never be use from third parties.
    2. To configure it according to current laws, regarding
       confidentiality of data collected and respect of your private life.

The choice is yours to accept or not to participate in these analytics
measurement

   IFRAME:
   http://www.libellule-arts.fr/piwik/index.php?module=CoreAdminHome&actio
   n=optOut&language=fr

Cookies

List of cookies used by Hesper

   Cookie Name :sideed367a4 Used for :This cookie keeps the information
   about the a user's browsing session. Lifetime :End of the browsing
   session
   Cookie Name :_pk_id Used for :This cookie is created by the analytics
   tool. Lifetime :13 months
   Cookie Name :_pk_ses Used for :This cookie is created by the analytics
   tool. Lifetime :End of the browsing session
   Cookie Name :cc_cookie_accept Used for :This cookie is created by the
   cookies control management system. Lifetime :12 months
   Cookie Name :cc_cookie_decline Used for :This cookie is created by the
   cookies control management system. Lifetime :End of the browsing
   session

List of cookies used by third parties

   Cookie Name :NID Used for :Google use some cookies on every page with
   Google Map App. Although we have no control over cookies used by
   Google, which are used to collect more information on the number of
   users and user behavior. Lifetime :6 months from its creation / from
   its update

